description:
### A limited edition of 121 floating and slightly glowing Magic Cubes.
##
Everyone knows them, almost everyone had one in their childhood. Now they are available here on Soonaverse in an IOTA Shimmer Assembly Edition, except for one of them.  
##
**Rarity:**  
- \- 1 very special Magic Cube
- \- 12 completed Magic Cubes floating horizontally
- \- 12 completed Magic Cubes floating tilted
- \- 12 completely messed up Magic Cubes
- \- 84 almost completed Magic Cubes
##
One day after the collection has sold out, the owner of the unique very special Magic Cube will be given my ultra NF3 set #992 for a total price of 3 Mi (1 Mi for each single #992 due to dust protection).
